snippet.title: [GOTY 2013 #2] Best VGM 1509 - Antichamber - Suite II (Short Version)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1467 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xWQOYiYHZ2w

Soundtrack: http://siddharthabarnhoorn.bandcamp.com/album/antichamber

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
Antichamber (2013)
Suite II (Short Version)
Siddhartha Barnhoorn
